descriptionHtml:
-No longer supported-

Just two new races right now, one is based around a pure physical fighting type and the other is mainly physical with some magic. Based off the nord body with use of most facial parts. Should be compatible with any body mod. 

The box is in Sleeping Giant Inn in Riverwood.

Please report any bugs and feel free to post pictures.
This is my first uploaded mod.

-WiP-
Balanced weapons
Camp to set up race
New weapons
New armor
NPC\'s with scripts (Gods included)


-Done-
Amazon race and items
Brute race and items



-Bugs-
Amazon chest piece not showing in box.
